                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7280" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0734</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8334 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破则立，不破则废？——嘉谷环保的破局困境</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Innovation ensures success and conservatism spells failure? ——The Dilemma of Jiagu Environmental Protection</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王建中，杨漫，喻俊芝，赵玲清，王萌伊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南嘉谷环保有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">嘉谷环保；技术创新；逆向混改</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jiagu Environmental Protection, technological innovation, reverse mixed ownership reform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南嘉谷环保有限公司是云南省内一家专门从事生态环境治理、环保工程设计与施工、生态厕所改造、蔬菜垃圾处理的中小型环保公司。经过十多年辛勤付出，云南嘉谷环保有限公司已成为生态厕所研发行业的领头企业之一。但是，目前公司产品面临着缺乏竞争力、利润下滑、市场份额下降的经营困境。在国家积极推进混合所有制改革的背景下，公司高层想利用逆向混改的方式引入国有资本，缓解企业融资约束和市场准入约束，促进企业技术创新。为了进一步扭转公司困境、提高市场竞争力，嘉谷环保是否应顺势进行逆向混改呢？本案例旨在引导学生从国家宏观政策出发，对具体案例企业逆向混改的动因进行分析和思考，掌握中小型民营科技型企业逆向混改的可行性、必要性，试图为民营科技型企业的混改找到合适自身的发展引擎。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Yunnan Jiagu Environmental Protection Limited Liability Company is a small and medium-sized environmental protection company in Yunnan Province specializing in ecological environment management, environmental protection engineering design and construction, ecological toilet transformation, vegetable waste treatment. After more than ten years of hard work, Yunnan Jiagu Environmental Protection Limited Liability Company has become one of the most outstanding companies in the research and development industry of ecological toilets.  However, the company&#39;s products are facing the business dilemma of lack of competitiveness, profit decline and market share decline. Under the background of the country actively promoting the mixed ownership reform, the company&#39;s senior management wants to use the reverse mixed reform to introduce state-owned capital, ease the financing constraints and market access constraints, and promote the technological innovation of the enterprise. In order to further reverse the company&#39;s predicament and improve the market competitiveness, should Jiagu environmental protection take advantage of the trend of reverse mixed reform? The purpose of this case is to guide students to analyze and think about the reasons for reverse mixing reform of specific enterprises from the perspective of national macro policies, to master the feasibility and necessity of reverse mixing reform of small and medium-sized private technology enterprises, and to try to find a suitable development engine for the mixed reform of private technology enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《技术创新管理》、《创新及创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术创新的管理因素:研发模式、人力资源、创新文化；逆向混改的动因:特殊的政治影响力、丰富的生产资料、优秀的公司治理能力；逆向混改的作用机理:公司治理、融资约束</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-04</td>
                            </tr>
